rows.label: tlk41700121_01_msg0001
rows.name:
What d'you want? This is a woodcraft
workshop. It's no place for kids.

rows.label: tlk41700121_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, what we do here is we take wood
from Gulan trees and prepare it for
a variety of uses.

rows.label: tlk41700121_01_msg0003
rows.name:
For instance, we build frames of
Puzzletree Wood strengthened with
Muscle Branches for use in buildings.

rows.label: tlk41700121_01_msg0004
rows.name:
It's a pretty tricky process, so I
wouldn't advise it, but...I guess you
can try your hand if you like?

rows.label: tlk41700121_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Good call. It's a bit of a dangerous job
to try out of curiosity alone.
